<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
		Hi <%= @recipient %>,
    </p>
	<p>
		This message is to inform you that the following comment has been made on your entry.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>
		Entry Title: <%= @title %><br/>
		Created: <% @entry.created_at %><br/>
	</p>
	<p>
		Comment: <%= @comment.comment %><br/>
		Author: <%= User.find(@comment.user_id).email %><br/>
		Added: <%= @comment.created_at %><br/>
    </p>
	<p>
		For more details please log into your account:<br/>
		<%= @url %><br/>
	</p>
	<p>
		You will receive another email shortly informing you once your submission has been reviewed.<br/>
	</p>
    <p>
		Thank you for your contribution,<br/>
		VR Knowledgebase<br/>
		http://www.vr-knowledgebase.org/
	</p>
  </body>
</html>
